data.description: This home has a 6.125% ASSUMABLE FHA mortgage interest rate! Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque community of Spring Grove Plantation in Moncks Corner. This immaculate single-family residence, built in 2019, offers the perfect blend of modern living and timeless charm. Situated on a level corner lot spanning approximately 0.15 acres, this home boasts privacy, convenience, and a host of desirable features. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the open and inviting floor plan. The heart of the home features a spacious living area, perfect for entertaining family and friends. The well-appointed kitchen boasts a gas range and gleaming stainless steel appliances, making it a chef's delight. The master bedroom is a serene retreat with ample space,while the two additional bedrooms offer flexibility for guest accommodations, a home office or a cozy nursery. Two full bathrooms provide convenience and comfort for all. Step outside to your private oasis, where a 6-foot privacy fence encloses the backyard, creating a secure environment for pets and play. Enjoy year-round outdoor living on the screened-in back porch, ideal for morning coffee or evening relaxation. Nestled within the sought-after Spring Grove Plantation community, this home offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful suburban lifestyle while being just a short drive away from the heart of Moncks Corner. You'll have easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning single-story residence your forever home. With its modern amenities, impeccable condition, and prime location, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories. Schedule a showing today and make this house your new home sweet home!
